OL,7,FDetective Constable Sean Downey from
OL,8,FLeicestershire Police said: "Had his
OL,9,Fex-partner not found these images and
OL,10,Fcontacted police, there's little doubt
OL,11,Fin my mind his offending could've
OL,12,Fcontinued to this very day.
